<bibRefCitation id="540B4B28E2628171CA00897FEE6F5D42" author="Kim, S. - K. &amp; Han, H. - Y." box="[811,1035,1819,1846]" pageId="20" pageNumber="517" pagination="255 - 291" refId="ref13368" refString="Kim, S. - K., Han, H. - Y. 2001. A systematic study of the genera Adapsilia and Parageloemyia in Korea (Diptera, Tephritoidea, Pyrgotidae). Insecta Koreana, 18 (3), 255 - 291." type="journal article" year="2001">Kim &amp; Han (2001)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
